[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Bass music playing ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=1"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=5"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=7"
  },
  {
    "text": "Simon Goldrei: Hello. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "This session is all about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to transition media gaplessly with HLS. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Simon and I'm a member of the Streaming Media team ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "here at Apple! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you utilize AVQueuePlayer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "or would like to offer your customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "a seamless, Up Next-style playback of HLS items ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your application? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you want to present your media with the continuity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "that the producer intended? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "Can we support our customers by providing an experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "to enjoy our media for longer? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "If yes, then you've tuned in to the best session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "to learn how you can now transition HLS items gaplessly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's our agenda. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll survey some of the engaging media experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can deliver with this new feature, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll detail the media authoring requirements, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll step through some playlist examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=61"
  },
  {
    "text": "highlighting best practices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we'll end with a demo. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=65"
  },
  {
    "text": "The benefits of transitioning between HLS-backed AVPlayerItems ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "in an AVQueuePlayer are straightforward. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "Until now, the point of transition ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "could be a little jarring; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "anything from an audible glitch to a momentary visual hiccup ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "or even an indication of indeterminate buffering. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "Gapless item transitions maintain a bond ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "that your application provides between the customer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "Perhaps you recall the phrase \"don't touch that dial.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can build an episodic treatment ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "that seamlessly transitions from the end of one episode ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=100"
  },
  {
    "text": "into the start of another. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "Gapless transitions permit the ability to replicate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "the seamless track-to-track album experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "that we've long enjoyed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "When doing this, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "we're delivering a more correct reproduction ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "of what may have been live or intentionally authored. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can deliver an experience that is unbroken ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "and uninterrupted. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can replicate linear programming. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=127"
  },
  {
    "text": "But we can also provide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "a dynamic and perhaps even interactive experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "that takes the viewer from one task or scene ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "and directly segues into the next. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "Consider a transition between a set of workouts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "or other instructional media. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "With gapless transitions we can now, programmatically, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "stitch scenes of an audiovisual sequence ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "while maintaining accurate continuity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can add reps... ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "...or add a cooldown, to the workout. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can achieve all of this ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "while still delivering media with all the benefits ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "of adaptive bitrate media streaming over HTTP. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course, we use this, too! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "New features of Apple Music deliver content via HLS ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "and achieve a gapless transition between each song. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "We're very excited to bring this to our customers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we'd like to offer this to your customers, too. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's now take detailed look at the authoring requirements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "you need to incorporate to affect the same item transitions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your HLS content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "By providing -- in your HLS manifests -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "variants that offer audio-format continuity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "between sequential items, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're enabling a gapless transition. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your content should provide variants that match ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "the following audio media traits: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "the use of FairPlay Streaming, the audio codec -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "specified by the codecs attribute of the Stream tag -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the channel count, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=217"
  },
  {
    "text": "as specified by the Channels attribute of the Media tag. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "Note that if you decide to offer audio renditions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "at different sample rates and bit depth, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "you may inhibit the gapless transition. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "The same advice to provide a match ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "and maintain continuity applies to these traits, too. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "Which is to say, to achieve a gapless transition, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "be sure to offer equivalent audio media in each variant ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "for consecutively enqueued items. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=244"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, when authoring your media, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "please adhere to CMAF authoring guidance. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "CMAF stands for \"common media application format.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this MPEG specification, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "there is a specific recommendation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "to use an edit list to signal the presence of priming ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=263"
  },
  {
    "text": "and remainder frames. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's now look at a simple example ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "by inspecting the master variant playlists ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "of two candidate items. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this HLS manifest ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "I've offered four audiovisual variants: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=279"
  },
  {
    "text": "a pair of 720p variants and a pair of 1080p variants. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=283"
  },
  {
    "text": "Within each pair, I offer a variant encoded ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the High-Efficiency Advanced Audio Codec, HE_AAC, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "and another with AAC Low Complexity, or AAC_LC. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this example, consider that playback conditions support ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=302"
  },
  {
    "text": "the selection of the 720p video paired with HE_AAC. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=305"
  },
  {
    "text": "As playback nears the end, the AVQueuePlayer will, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=311"
  },
  {
    "text": "at least initially, select the similarly encoded variant ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "offered in the subsequent item. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is true even if network conditions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "now support a higher-quality tier. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "Servicing the gapless transition is a higher priority ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "than choosing a high quality when transitioning gaplessly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "As playback proceeds, the adaptive bitrate heuristics ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "are evaluated and, if the conditions persist, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "the player will seamlessly switch to that higher quality. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "Fantastic! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now suppose we didn't offer HE_AAC in item two. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "In that case, the AVQueuePlayer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "is unable to maintain audio continuity ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the gapless transition but is free to select ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "the most appropriate initial variant ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the playback conditions. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=360"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's say that we have authored our content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "to support a gapless transition. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=364"
  },
  {
    "text": "In that case, we should remind ourselves ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to use an AVQueuePlayer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we have a short code snippet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=371"
  },
  {
    "text": "We create two AVPlayerItems and enqueue them, in order, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "ahead of playback. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "Note that our items source from two different URLs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=379"
  },
  {
    "text": "After creating our AVQueuePlayer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "we can use the \"insert after\" method ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "to inform the queue player of the intended sequence. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "All that's left is to message \"play\".",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "An advanced technique I'd like to share with you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "permits the use of a single asset. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=406"
  },
  {
    "text": "From this asset, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=409"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can instantiate multiple AVPlayerItems. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can define different in and out points ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=414"
  },
  {
    "text": "on each distinct AVPlayerItem, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=417"
  },
  {
    "text": "prior to enqueuing in our AVQueuePlayer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": "Using the AVPlayerItem seekToTime method, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "we can define our in point. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then we can define our out point with forwardPlaybackEndTime. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=430"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's an illustration of this concept. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=434"
  },
  {
    "text": "Item one, two, and three are all sourced from the same AVAsset, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=437"
  },
  {
    "text": "consisting of the same three scenes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=441"
  },
  {
    "text": "They are distinct in that I have cued each ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "with different in points, using seekToTime, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "and defined distinct out points, using forwardPlaybackEndTime. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now I can enqueue these three otherwise identical items ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "into my AVQueuePlayer, and what I achieve ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=459"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a customized, dynamic sequence. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=462"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's see and hear gapless transitions in action ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=466"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a demo. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this demo, we will interactively stitch together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=470"
  },
  {
    "text": "three workout video streams. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=474"
  },
  {
    "text": "I've left the AVKit controls visible in each ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that you can really see these are distinct stream resources. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll start by showing a seamless playback of all three ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "and then we'll edit the sequence interactively. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=487"
  },
  {
    "text": "In your software, you can imagine offering the same -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=489"
  },
  {
    "text": "or perhaps perform the reordering -- programmatically. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=492"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=498"
  },
  {
    "text": "Right! Let's do a warm-up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=500"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Energetic electronic music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=502"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ready or not? Let's do a hills run. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=510"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Lively hip-hop music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's it! We're done. It's time for a cooldown. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=520"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=523"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Calm electronic music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=524"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=527"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can break a sweat just watching that. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=531"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm tempted to skip straight to the \"That's it, we're done,\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "and skip the hills run. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's a lot of that here in San Francisco. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=538"
  },
  {
    "text": "To do this, let's edit the order of our exercise sets. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll move the hills exercise to the top. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "This allows me to just do the warm-up ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "then immediately and gaplessly segue into the cooldown. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=550"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then I'll start by selecting the warm-up, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "now in the second position, as my first workout. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=561"
  },
  {
    "text": "Right! Let's do a warm-up. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Energetic electronic music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's it! We're done. It's time for a cooldown. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=573"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=575"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Calm electronic music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=576"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's summarize the key points ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=585"
  },
  {
    "text": "that we've learned in this session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=587"
  },
  {
    "text": "We've learned that to achieve gapless transitions using HLS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=589"
  },
  {
    "text": "we must provide variants in each item ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=593"
  },
  {
    "text": "that have matching audio formats. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=595"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then we saw how easy it is to instruct an AVQueuePlayer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=598"
  },
  {
    "text": "to perform the gapless transition ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=602"
  },
  {
    "text": "just by enqueuing items in sequence. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "We have one related session, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "where we introduce new APIs for variant discovery. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "You may find that session useful if your software or service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=613"
  },
  {
    "text": "cannot guarantee the items of matching audio format. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=616"
  },
  {
    "text": "I hope you've enjoyed this session ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "and enjoy the rest of this WWDC 2021. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=621"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=625"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10142/?time=627"
  }
]